            <p><strong>Privacy Policy Summary:</strong></p>
            <p>At Saivijay Art, we value your trust and prioritize secure transactions and information privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, share, and process your personal data on SaivijayArt.com.</p>
