        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>At Saivijay Art, we deeply value the trust you place in us and understand the significance of safeguarding your information and ensuring secure transactions. This Privacy Policy outlines how Saivijay Art collects, uses, shares, and processes your personal data on the SaivijayArt.com website (referred to as the "Platform").</p>

        <h2>Information Collection</h2>
        <p>When you use our Platform, we gather and store information provided by you. While certain sections of the Platform allow browsing without providing personal data, please note that our services are primarily offered within India, and your data will be processed and stored accordingly. By using our Platform, you agree to abide by our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.</p>
        
        <h2>Use of Your Information</h2>
        <p>We collect personal data such as email addresses, delivery addresses, and payment details when you create an account, transact with us, or participate in events. This information helps us enhance your experience, provide personalized offers, and improve our services. Your interactions on our Platform, including messages, feedback, and social media engagement, may also be collected and used for internal purposes.</p>

        <h2>Third-Party Partners</h2>
        <p>Saivijay Art may collaborate with third-party partners for certain services such as loyalty programs and specialized categories. These partners may collect personal data directly from you, and their privacy policies will govern such data collection.</p>
        
        <h2>Data Usage and Protection</h2>
        <p>We utilize your personal data to process orders, deliver products/services, communicate with you, and personalize your experience. Saivijay Art maintains physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards to protect your information. However, users should acknowledge the inherent risks associated with data transmission over the internet.</p>
        
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, and update your personal data on the Platform. You may withdraw consent or opt-out of certain communications. Please note that withdrawal of consent may affect your access to certain features or services.</p>
        
        <h2>Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may periodically update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in information practices. Significant updates will be communicated through the Platform or via email.</p>

